        Rubric </name>
          <val><![CDATA[<p style="">For this item, a full-credit 1 point response includes:</p><p style="">&#xA0;</p><ul style="padding-left:1.5000em; "><li><p style="">Student selects “Other studies show that students need about the same amount of time in any program to review topics such as math.” </p><p style="">AND</p></li><li><p style="">Student selects “More time needs to be spent on social studies education.” </p></li></ul>]]></val>
